items.summary: 症状/環境が近い投稿。エラー文と権限・prefix・PATHが焦点になりやすい。

I summarized a step-by-step checklist (with common mistakes + fixes) here: https://mikann20041029.github.io/solve-multi-python-modulenotfounderror-202602161629/
If you can share OS + Node/npm versions and the exact command, it's easier to pinpoint.
